N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4405.7 - State lottery

State Regulations

Where feasible, a corporation shall maintain a State
lottery outlet at a branch office at the direction of the commission and shall
receive reasonable compensation therefor on a strict cost reimbursement
basis. Notes
